Description: ## Solnado
        
        Tornado HTTP Client for Solr.
        
        
        ### Example
        Example usage with Solr cloud:
        
            from solnado import SolrClient
            import tornado.ioloop
            iol = tornado.ioloop.IOLoop.current()
        
            client = SolrClient() # default to localhost:8983
            res = yield gen.Task(client.create_collection, 'foo')
            print res.body
        
            iol.start()
